snippet.title: Frip and Froop's Logical Labyrinth DX Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready for science! Frip and Froop's Logical Labyrinth DX launches February 6th, 2025! 

Wishlist it here! http://store.steampowered.com/app/2499740/

Frip and Froop's Logical Labyrinth DX is a remake of our very first title with improved graphics, design, story, music, and more! With over 150 brand new and remastered puzzles, Frip and Froop's Logical Labyrinth DX is bringing you the world of tomorrow, today!

Featuring the voice talents of Dino Andrade, Kelly Jensen, and Petros L. Ioannou!
